The Beplain Mung Bean Pore Clay Mask is a skincare product designed to provide a gentle yet effective solution for deep cleansing and pore care. It features mung bean extract, known for its soothing and purifying properties, which helps to remove excess sebum, unclog pores, and calm irritated skin.
How to use?
Apply an even layer to clean, dry skin, avoiding the eye and lip areas. Leave on for 10–15 minutes until the mask dries. Rinse off thoroughly with lukewarm water. Use 1–2 times a week:)
